quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  57,25,"Sellii Men nulirii Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen hujjaaji …ďanngu…ói, Men jippindinani …ďe Defte e sariyaare, fii no yim…ďe …ďen √Īii…ďira e nun…óal. Men jippini kadi njamndi ndin, ndi doole tii…óu…óe woni e mun; ko kayri tafir…óe jogaaji, ko non kadi nafooje wonirani yim…ďe …ďen e majje ka mecce ma…ď…ďe, e fii kadi no Allah anndira anndal fe√Ī√Īinirangol jeyaa…ďe …ďen, …ďen walloo…ďe Mo e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen ka wirnii. Pelelt, Allah ko Jom cemmbe, Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake. Fii huunde ronkinŇčtaa Mo."
  57,26,"Gom…óii Men nulii Nuuhu e Ibraahiima (yo …ďe his), Men wa…ói e geyngol ma…ď…ďe ngol Annabaaku e Defte tellinaa…óe. Hino jeyanoo e geyngol ma…ď…ďe ngol feewu…ďe e laawol foccingol ngol, hawri e peewal, ko …óuu…óunoo kon e ma…ď…ďe ko yaltunoo…ďe e …ófotaare Allah."
  57,27,"Refti Men jokkintini …ďe Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen, Men nuliri …ďe kala e mofte mun. Men jokkintiniri …ďe Iisaa ge…óal Maryama on, Men okki mo Linjiila, Men wa…ói e …ďer…óe gom…óim…ďe mo …ďen jokki mo : yurmeende e giggol, …ďe yi…óindiri …ďe yurmondiri. ∆Āe sincoyi fantingol ka diina ma…ď…ďe, …ďe acci yoga e ko Allah daginannoo …ďe immorde e desal e dakamme, e hoore Men …óa…ď…ďiraa …ďe …óum, ko kam…ďe fawitii …óum sincugol ka diina. Ko Men …óa…ď…ďirnoo …ďe Menen, ko jokkugol welayee Allah on, kono …ďe wa…óaali …óum. Men okki mbarjaari gom…óim…ďe …ďen e ma…ď…ďe. Ko …óuu…óunoo kon e ma…ď…ďe, ko yaltirnoo…ďe e …óoftaare Allah fennugol ko Nulaa…óo Muhammadu addunoo kon."
  57,28,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe Allah gollitiri sari'a Makko on ! Huliree Allah …óoftagol yamaruyeeji Makko …óin, wo…ó…óitoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, gom…óinon Nulaa…óo Makko on; O okkay on ge…ďe …ói…ói e mbarjaari gom…óingol mon ngol Muhammadu e Nulaa…ďe adinoo…ďe …ďen, O wa…óana on kadi annoora …ďe ndayginorton ka aduna mon e ka lummboygol Siraate √Ďalnde Darngal, O haforana on kadi bakkatuuji mon …óin hara O nanngitirtaa on …ói. Pellet, Allah senii…óo On, ko Haforanoowo jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen, Hinnotoo…óo …ďe."
  57,29,"Ko Men …ďannginirani on …ďural Amen mawngal ngal e kon ko Men marani on onon muumuni'en, immorde e mbrajaari sowaandi, ko fii no Alyahhuda e Annasaara ka yim…ďe Defte anndira wonnde …ďe hattanaa hay huunde e …ďural Allah ngal, sakko …ďe ye…óa mo …ďe yi…óani, …ďe …óawa ngal mo …ďe yi…ói …óawude, …ďe annda kadi pellet, …ďural ngal ko e juu…óe Allah woni, Himo ye…óa ngal mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen. Pellet, Allah ko Jom …ďural mawngal ngal O heertinanta mo O muuyani e jeyaa…ďe Makko …ďen."